com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.merge

Class DefaultDesignMerger

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.merge.AbstractDesignMerger
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.merge.DefaultDesignMerger

  • public class DefaultDesignMerger
extends AbstractDesignMerger
    Provides a basic design merging behavior when merging designs. If no other design merger is implemented, MergeDesigns.mergeDesigns(com.xilinx.rapidwright.design.Design...) is used by default.
